---
title: Cheat's Baked Chicken & Red Lentil Dhal with Silverbeet & Yoghurt
description: No wonder dhal is the darling of Indian home cooking – it's nutritious, versatile, easy to make and brimming with flavour. Here,
we're adding tender pieces of chicken, veggies and a dollop of yoghurt.
